                        <note rend="inline" type="source">817.1051/260: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Minister in Nicaragua</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Eberhardt</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-02-15T18:00:00-05:00">February 15, 1929—6
                                p.m.</date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>27. Withhold action on Department’s 26, February 14, 6 p.m., pending
                            further instructions.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi></signed></closer>
